data.description: Experience the epitome of luxury living on the First Fairway of the Hawks Prairie Golf Course. This Campus Peak 5 bedroom + office/2.5 bath home boasts an impeccable design and exquisite features, truly paradise. Inside you'll find elegance and sophistication with espresso cabinetry, quartz counters, stainless steel appliances and engineered hardwood floors. The gas fireplace creates a cozy ambiance, perfect for relaxing after a day on the greens. The primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a huge 5-piece ensuite with soaking tub, slate floors and a walk-in closet. Situated on a dead-end street, this property offers both tranquility and convenience with easy access to I-5 & JBLM. You won't want to miss this opportunity!
